descriptions:
Currently LocalTransportController makes an assumption that all the participants in the group are on the same itinerary. Many of our local travel providers limit reservations to 4 people. To accommodate larger groups we need to have multiple flight itineraries on one reservation. 

Group spaceship rental should be a collection of itineraries with a number of carriers that the user selects stored as one data structure. 

{panel:title=NOTE|borderStyle=dashed|borderColor=#ccc|titleBGColor=#F7D6C1|bgColor=#FFFFCE} 
If a user is using a large local transport vendor, we should still provide the option to book a personal spacecraft for anyone in the group. That reservation should not be double booked on the larger transport vendor. 
{panel}

